Package gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2.io

Input-output utilities for RDF models.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BlankNodesPolicy Defines a policy regarding how to create blank node identifiers while parsing an input.
RdfIO A class containing utilities for reading and writing RDF content in various serialization formats.
RdfIO.InputWithBase A class that performs the actual parsing and adds the produced triples to a model.
RdfIO.InputWithoutBase A class that handles part of the workflow of a parsing; particularly the part that the user optionally specifies the base URI to be used.
RdfIO.ModelWriterWithBase A class that handles part of the workflow of serialization; particularly the part that the actual serialization is performed.
RdfIO.ModelWriterWithoutBase A class that handles part of the workflow of serialization; particularly the part that the user optionally specifies the base URI to be used.
 

Enum Summary
Format The format of an RDF serialization.
 

Package gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2.io Description

Input-output utilities for RDF models.

See RdfIO for details on how to read input to models or write models, using various serialization formats.
